{"tha-ap133:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap133:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap133:0.3":"Sobhitattheraapadana ","tha-ap133:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap133:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap133:1.3":"Mahato janakayassa, ","tha-ap133:1.4":"deseti amatam padam. ","tha-ap133:2.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap133:2.2":"vacasabhimudiritam; ","tha-ap133:2.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap133:2.4":"ekaggo asaham tada. ","tha-ap133:3.1":"‘Yatha samuddo udadhinamaggo, ","tha-ap133:3.2":"Neru naganam pavaro siluccayo; ","tha-ap133:3.3":"Tatheva ye cittavasena vattare’, ","tha-ap133:3.4":"Na buddhananassa kalam upenti te. ","tha-ap133:4.1":"Dhammavidhim thapetvana, ","tha-ap133:4.2":"buddho karuniko isi; ","tha-ap133:4.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap133:4.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap133:5.1":"‘Yo so nanam pakittesi, ","tha-ap133:5.2":"buddhamhi lokanayake; ","tha-ap133:5.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap133:5.4":"duggatim na gamissati. ","tha-ap133:6.1":"Kilese jhapayitvana, ","tha-ap133:6.2":"ekaggo susamahito; ","tha-ap133:6.3":"Sobhito nama namena, ","tha-ap133:6.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap133:7.1":"Pannase kappasahasse, ","tha-ap133:7.2":"sattevasum yasuggata; ","tha-ap133:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap133:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap133:8.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap133:8.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap133:8.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap133:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap133:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap133:9.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap133:9.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap133:9.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap133:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sobhito thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap133:11.1":"Sobhitattherassapadanam pathamam. "}